quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  26,123,Aadunim‚Äô (Annabi Hudu niriba) daa labsi Naawuni tuumba  íirinima
  26,124,"Saha shőĶli b…õ mabia Hudu ni daa yőĶli ba: ‚ÄúDi ni b…ĒŇč…Ē, yi ku zo Naawuni"
  26,125,‚ÄúAchiika! Mani ny…õla tuun‚Äô so Ňčun mali y…õmbahiga n-zaŇč tin ya.‚ÄĚ
  26,126,"‚ÄúDinzu…£u, zom ya Naawuni ka doli ma.‚ÄĚ"
  26,127,"‚ÄúYaha! M-bi b…Ēhiri ya sanyo‚Äô shőĶli, n-ka sanyoo na…£ila binnamda Duuma sani.‚ÄĚ"
  26,128,"‚ÄúDi ni b…ĒŇč…Ē, yi miőĶrila yiliwa…£ila tamdi zoli din kam be soli zu…£u, ka ny…õla ban kpőĶrita?‚ÄĚ"
  26,129,‚ÄúKa yi gbibi yiliwa…£ila maa kamani y shiri ny…õla ban y…õn kpalim (Dunia puuni) la.‚ÄĚ
  26,130,"‚ÄúYi mi yi ti y…õn gbahi ninvu…£u sh…õba (yi dimba), yi gbahiri ba mi ka ny…õla ban kpahiri yőĶ…£iri tariga.‚ÄĚ"
  26,131,"‚ÄúDinzu…£u, zom ya Naawuni ka doli ma.‚ÄĚ"
  26,132,‚ÄúYaha! Zom ya (Duuma so) Ňäun yolsi ya ni yi ni mi sh…õli.‚ÄĚ
  26,133,‚ÄúO (Naawuni) yolsi ya mi ni biŇčk…Ēbri mini bihi.‚ÄĚ
  26,134,‚ÄúNi puri mini kobilnina.‚ÄĚ
  26,135,‚ÄúAchiika! Mani z…Ērila dabsi‚Äô titali la daazaaba n-tiri ya.‚ÄĚ
  26,136,"Ka b…õ yőĶli: ‚ÄúDi ny…õla yim n-ti ti, a niŇč wa‚Äôazu, bee a ka ban niŇčdi wa‚Äôazu ni.‚ÄĚ"
  26,137,"(Ka b…õ lahi y…õli):‚ÄúŇä…Ē (Alkur‚Äôaani) maa pa shőĶli m-pahila kurumbuni nima (daadaa nima) ta‚Äôada.‚ÄĚ"
  26,138,‚ÄúYaha! Ti pala ninvu…£u shőĶba b…õ ni y…õn ti niŇč azaaba.‚ÄĚ
  26,139,"Ka b…õ labsi o (Annabi Hudu)  íirilana, ka Ti (Tinim‚Äô Naawuni) niŇč ba hallaka. Achiika! Ňä…Ē maa puuni mali kpahimbu. Amaa! B…õ (chőĶfurinima) pam pala ban ti Naawuni yőĶlimaŇčli"
  26,140,"Yaha! (Yaa nyini Annabi)! Achiika! A Duuma (Naawuni) ny…õla NyőĶŇčda, Zaadali Namb…Ēzobonaa"